            "notes": "The main focus of this control deck is to utilize Atraxa, Grand Unifier's abilities to control the board and disrupt the opponent's strategy. The deck is packed with counterspells like Force Spike, Mana Leak, and spell-snaring effects to stop threats before they hit the battlefield. It also includes powerful board wipes like Toxic Deluge and Supreme Verdict to maintain control. The deck aims to control the game through card advantage with cards like Teferi, Time Raveler and Tamiyo, Inquisitive Student while also utilizing versatile removal like Swords to Plowshares and Abrupt Decay. The mana base is carefully constructed to ensure consistent access to all colors and includes utility lands like Boseiju, Who Endures and Mystic Sanctuary for added advantage."
